text: "Around the World" is the second and final single from Dutch singer Natalie La Rose. It features American rapper Fetty Wap, who co-wrote the song with its producers Marco "MAG" Borrero, Ilya Salmanzadeh, and Max Martin, with additional writing from Savan Kotecha, Rickard Goransson, and DJ Frank E. The single reached number 3 on the US Billboard Bubbling Under Hot 100 Singles chart. == Music video == The music video was released on July 24, 2015 on La Rose's Vevo account. ==Charts== {|class="wikitable sortable plainrowheaders" style="text-align:center;" |- !
